  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Objective: To compare 2-dimensional and 3-dimensional ultrasound measurements with the actual
      myomas volume after surgical removal, to clinically test the validity and usability of 3D
      ultrasound technology as opposed to conventional 2D real-time ultrasound and to assess the
      reliability of different ultrasound methods to measure volume of uterine fibroids.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
